About this hotel

Set in lavish Moroccan-style villas amid palm tree-shaded gardens, this premium resort is 6 km from Jemaa el-Fnaa square and 7 km from the 16th-century El Badi Palace.

Check-in time: 3:00 PM
Check-out time: 12:00 PM

    Annakhil

    The sprawling suburb of Annakhil includes golf courses and palm groves, with paths and horse-carriage tours through 100,000 trees at El Palmeral. Inside that park is Musée de la Palmeraie, showing a century of Moroccan paintings in a 1940s colonial farmhouse. MACAAL is a more modern space, displaying pan-African art. Residential areas have casual tagine restaurants, while resort hotels have chic bars and bistros.

    About this hotel

    Set in lavish Moroccan-style villas amid palm tree-shaded gardens, this premium resort is 6 km from Jemaa el-Fnaa square and 7 km from the 16th-century El Badi Palace. …

    Stylish 1- to 2-bedroom villas have domed ceilings and mosaic tile floors, and feature living areas with fireplaces, and courtyards with garden views. Some offer heated pools and/or private butler service. All come with free Wi-Fi and flat-screens, plus minibars and espresso machines.

    Amenities include 2 refined restaurants and a bar, as well as an exercise room, tennis courts and an outdoor pool. There's also a spa with a hot tub and 2 hammams.
